CodeCompletionResponse Model - Response to a code completion request.
state string Enum
State of the code completion. Options : ['End']
version number
Version of the response.
payload string Array
Code completion suggestions.
payloadType string
Type of the payload.
Example 
{
  "state": "End",
  "version": 0,
  "payload": [
    "string"
  ],
  "payloadType": "string"
}
